{"tid":193134,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【韓流】SM香港練習生遭起底 18歲黃旭熙兩女爭住咀","createTime":"2017-04-09T05:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T02:17:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c87c848dbe577e9a5c3bb8fc612e3ed3a1a7b5","tid":193134,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170408/large/1491643694_9578.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170408%2Flarge%2F1491643694_9578.jpg&h=9f9cdda2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旗下擁有Super Junior、少女時代、EXO等組合嘅韓國SM事務所，近年推出一個練習生團體SM Rookies，等粉絲可以認識SM嘅練習生，睇住佢哋準備出道嘅過程。上星期，SM Rookies就公佈新成員，就係嚟自香港嘅18歲男生黃旭熙（Lucas）。<br />\n<br />\n1999年出世嘅Lucas於本年1月剛滿18歲，據知媽媽係泰國人，讀書時人緣幾好好，運動好叻，前年出席SM嘅全球選秀時被工作人員睇中，大約一年前成為SM練習生。因為身高超過1米8，加上外型討好，唔少網民都睇好佢可以出道，而Lucas早前更參與NCT成員Ten嘅《夢中夢》MV拍攝。<br />\n不過Lucas嘅造型照一被公開，佢就極速被網民起底，搵出佢極有異性緣，被爆多張跟女生嘅合照，當中更有一張係被兩名女生同時咀嘅相，唔少人擔心佢太好嘅異性緣會拖累其事業，未出道就被out。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170408/large/1491643699_d29e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170408%2Flarge%2F1491643699_d29e.png&h=f23a031d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過Lucas就被爆異性緣非常好（網上圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170409/56538385\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170409%2F56538385&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=2b591901\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170409%2F56538385&h=12ed9fec\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170409/56538385</a>"},{"pid":"2afc85ad33a4dedcaee9a3052110ef6e40c1cf07","tid":193134,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2